    <item>
      <title>尽管利润率下降，中国大型银行利润仍增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/china-s-mega-banks-post-profit-gains-even-as-margins-deteriorate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管已经处于历史低位的净息差继续恶化，但中国最大的国有银行在第三季度仍实现利润增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/china-s-mega-banks-post-profit-gains-even-as-margins-deteriorate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:47:25 GMT</pubDate>
