      <title>腾讯支持的 Airwallex 寻求 60 亿美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/tencent-backed-airwallex-seeks-funding-eyes-6-billion-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，金融科技公司 Airwallex 正在与投资者洽谈在新一轮融资中筹集约 2 亿美元以资助其增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/tencent-backed-airwallex-seeks-funding-eyes-6-billion-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:03:15 GMT</pubDate>
